WEBVTT

00:01.517 --> 00:03.684
There is a clinic in Toronto.

00:03.719 --> 00:06.620
Their work is untested,
the risks undocumented.

00:06.655 --> 00:07.955
Emma: <i>I can't do this.</i>
<i>I need help.</i>

00:07.990 --> 00:09.690
- I don't... I don't know.
- Please.

00:09.724 --> 00:11.024
Woman: <i>This ended up</i>
<i>in the mailroom.</i>

00:11.058 --> 00:12.525
<i>Who the hell is Rosebud?</i>

00:12.560 --> 00:14.227
Gentlemen, I wanted to present
this redevelopment plan

00:14.261 --> 00:16.529
in person because
of its tremendous scope.

00:16.563 --> 00:18.763
All this only comes into play if
you can get folks out of there

00:18.798 --> 00:20.198
<i>for the demo, though, right?</i>

00:20.232 --> 00:22.600
Your banks hold title
on hundreds of foreclosures.

00:22.635 --> 00:24.735
If the market rebounds,
we won't be able to sell.

00:24.770 --> 00:27.138
We have a no-fail
completion date of two years.

00:27.172 --> 00:29.572
Every family in good standing
will be welcomed back

00:29.607 --> 00:32.008
when the construction for the new
Lennox Gardens is completed.

00:32.042 --> 00:33.542
Man over phone: <i>The Gardens aren't</i>
<i>your business.</i>

00:33.576 --> 00:34.777
- Quit.
- You wanna fuck with me?

00:34.811 --> 00:35.978
You're fucking
with your own mayor.

00:36.012 --> 00:38.613
( Gasping ) No!

00:38.648 --> 00:41.049
Moderator: <i>Welcome to the great</i>
<i>gubernatorial debate.</i>

00:41.083 --> 00:42.083
Woman:
<i>Mr. Zajac,</i>

00:42.117 --> 00:43.985
who is the woman
in the picture?

00:44.019 --> 00:45.920
I'd rather not comment
on an unconfirmed photograph.

00:45.954 --> 00:49.890
Man: Did you have an affair
with Alderman Ross' wife?

00:49.924 --> 00:53.125
I am the goddamn mayor
of this motherfucking city

00:53.159 --> 00:54.960
and I want this hole fixed now!

00:58.231 --> 01:00.765
Where are we going, Tom?

